    <td valign="top" align="left">
		<font face="verdana" size="2">
		<b>Description:</b> <br>
		This is an undead fear spell. It will cause the undead to runaway. You can use this spell to get unwanted mobs off your back during a battle.
		</font>
	 </td>
	 <td rowspan="4" valign="top" align="right">
    
